data.description: Welcome to this charming tri-level home boasting a fresh and modern appeal throughout. The entire house features brand new neutral paint and new carpet, providing a clean slate for your personal touch. The remodeled kitchen is a highlight, showcasing elegant granite counters and sleek stainless steel appliances. The main floor welcomes you with a spacious living room and dining room, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying family gatherings. On the lower level, a cozy family room with a brick fireplace awaits, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. An optional office or 4th bedroom provides flexibility, complete with convenient access to the laundry room and garage. A full bathroom on the lower level adds convenience for both residents and guests. Heading to the second level, you'll find three bedrooms, each offering comfort and style. These bedrooms share a full bathroom, emphasizing practicality and functionality for daily living. Step outside into the backyard oasis, where an above-ground pool and deck beckon for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. Whether you're hosting a summer barbecue or simply unwinding after a long day, this backyard retreat adds an extra layer of appeal to this fantastic tri-level home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home, where thoughtful updates and a well-designed layout come together seamlessly. Woodland/Warren Schools.
